---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Skief Labs" description="Built by someone who learned systems out of necessity. Learn about Skief Labs, founder Sardar Azimov, and our approach to B2B systems.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-linen pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Text -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="page-hero-title heading-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.8rem] text-navy mb-8 leading-[1.1] uppercase">
            Built from<br>necessity,<br>not theory.
          </h1>
          <div class="page-hero-body text-black text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
            <p>Skief Labs exists because growing businesses are routinely held together by people doing work that systems should handle — manual follow-ups, copied data, unclear ownership. Processes that sort of work, until growth breaks them. We've seen this pattern too many times to keep solving it one person at a time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right: Line chart graphic -->
        <div class="page-hero-image relative flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-full max-w-[420px] rounded-[10px] shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_#CFFF15] flex items-center justify-center p-8 md:p-10" style="background-color: #D9D9D9; aspect-ratio: 16/10;">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 400 200" class="w-full h-auto" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">

              <!-- "L" Axes -->
              <line x1="58" y1="22"  x2="58"  y2="165" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.55"/>
              <line x1="58" y1="165" x2="382" y2="165" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.55"/>

              <!-- Axis labels -->
              <text x="18" y="94" fill="#001D52" font-size="12" font-family="Nunito, sans-serif"
                    font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" opacity="0.8" transform="rotate(-90 18 94)">Output</text>
              <text x="220" y="181" fill="#001D52" font-size="12" font-family="Nunito, sans-serif"
                    font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" opacity="0.8">Time</text>

              <!-- Dashed grid lines -->
              <line x1="58" y1="65"  x2="382" y2="65"  stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="5,5" stroke-opacity="0.18"/>
              <line x1="58" y1="105" x2="382" y2="105" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="5,5" stroke-opacity="0.18"/>
              <line x1="58" y1="145" x2="382" y2="145" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="5,5" stroke-opacity="0.18"/>

              <!-- Manual Effort path (blue, zigzag) -->
              <path id="ab-me-line"
                d="M 58,163 L 78,142 L 96,156 L 116,132 L 135,150 L 154,126 L 173,145 L 192,120 L 211,138 L 231,114 L 250,132 L 269,110 L 287,127 L 306,113 L 325,124 L 344,111 L 363,121 L 381,112"
                stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"
                pathLength="400" stroke-dasharray="400" stroke-dashoffset="400"/>

              <!-- System Pipeline path (navy, S-curve sigmoid) -->
              <path id="ab-sp-line"
                d="M 58,163 C 270,163 270,24 381,24"
                stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"
                pathLength="400" stroke-dasharray="400" stroke-dashoffset="400"/>

              <!-- Manual Effort traveling dot (blue) -->
              <g id="ab-me-dot">
                <circle class="ab-me-radar" r="9"   fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.2"/>
                <circle                     r="6.5" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.8"/>
                <circle                     r="2.5" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              </g>

              <!-- System Pipeline traveling dot (navy) -->
              <g id="ab-sp-dot">
                <circle class="ab-sp-radar" r="9"   fill="none" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.2"/>
                <circle                     r="6.5" fill="none" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.8"/>
                <circle                     r="2.5" fill="#001D52"/>
              </g>

              <!-- Legend -->
              <line x1="58"  y1="191" x2="78"  y2="191" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-opacity="0.7"/>
              <text x="83"  y="196" fill="#0A60FF" font-size="11" font-family="Nunito, sans-serif" font-weight="600" opacity="0.85">Manual Effort</text>
              <line x1="200" y1="191" x2="220" y2="191" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <text x="225" y="196" fill="#001D52" font-size="11" font-family="Nunito, sans-serif" font-weight="600">System Pipeline</text>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <style>
            /*
              6s loop. Both lines draw left→right (dashoffset 400→0) from 4%–80%.
              Both dots travel their paths simultaneously (offset-distance 0%→100%).
              At 87% brief pause. 91% fade out. 92% instant invisible reset. 100% restart.
            */

            /* Line draw animations */
            @keyframes ab-sp-draw {
              0%, 2%  { stroke-dashoffset: 400; opacity: 0; }
              4%      { stroke-dashoffset: 398; opacity: 1; }
              80%     { stroke-dashoffset: 0;   opacity: 1; }
              87%     { stroke-dashoffset: 0;   opacity: 1; }
              91%     { stroke-dashoffset: 0;   opacity: 0; }
              92%     { stroke-dashoffset: 400; opacity: 0; }
              100%    { stroke-dashoffset: 400; opacity: 0; }
            }
            @keyframes ab-me-draw {
              0%, 2%  { stroke-dashoffset: 400; opacity: 0; }
              4%      { stroke-dashoffset: 398; opacity: 1; }
              80%     { stroke-dashoffset: 0;   opacity: 1; }
              87%     { stroke-dashoffset: 0;   opacity: 1; }
              91%     { stroke-dashoffset: 0;   opacity: 0; }
              92%     { stroke-dashoffset: 400; opacity: 0; }
              100%    { stroke-dashoffset: 400; opacity: 0; }
            }
            #ab-sp-line { animation: ab-sp-draw 6s linear 0.8s infinite backwards; }
            #ab-me-line { animation: ab-me-draw 6s linear 0.8s infinite backwards; }

            /* Dot motion paths */
            #ab-sp-dot {
              offset-path: path('M 58,163 C 270,163 270,24 381,24');
              offset-rotate: 0deg;
            }
            #ab-me-dot {
              offset-path: path('M 58,163 L 78,142 L 96,156 L 116,132 L 135,150 L 154,126 L 173,145 L 192,120 L 211,138 L 231,114 L 250,132 L 269,110 L 287,127 L 306,113 L 325,124 L 344,111 L 363,121 L 381,112');
              offset-rotate: 0deg;
            }

            /* Dot travel animations */
            @keyframes ab-sp-travel {
              0%, 2%    { offset-distance: 0%;   opacity: 0; }
              4%        { offset-distance: 0%;   opacity: 1; }
              80%       { offset-distance: 100%; opacity: 1; }
              87%       { offset-distance: 100%; opacity: 1; }
              91%       { offset-distance: 100%; opacity: 0; }
              92%, 100% { offset-distance: 0%;   opacity: 0; }
            }
            @keyframes ab-me-travel {
              0%, 2%    { offset-distance: 0%;   opacity: 0; }
              4%        { offset-distance: 0%;   opacity: 1; }
              80%       { offset-distance: 100%; opacity: 1; }
              87%       { offset-distance: 100%; opacity: 1; }
              91%       { offset-distance: 100%; opacity: 0; }
              92%, 100% { offset-distance: 0%;   opacity: 0; }
            }
            #ab-sp-dot { animation: ab-sp-travel 6s linear 0.8s infinite backwards; }
            #ab-me-dot { animation: ab-me-travel 6s linear 0.8s infinite backwards; }

            /* Continuous radar rings on both dots */
            .ab-sp-radar, .ab-me-radar {
              transform-box: fill-box;
              transform-origin: center;
            }
            @keyframes ab-radar {
              0%   { transform: scale(1);   opacity: 0.65; }
              100% { transform: scale(2.4); opacity: 0;    }
            }
            .ab-sp-radar { animation: ab-radar 1.4s ease-out 0.8s infinite backwards; }
            .ab-me-radar { animation: ab-radar 1.4s ease-out 0.8s infinite backwards; }
          </style>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR POINT OF VIEW -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="page-hero-next grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]" style="color: #001D52;">
            Our point of view
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4 text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Most B2B companies don't stall because of bad strategy or bad people.</p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-black">They stall because their systems never evolved as the business did.</p>
          <p>As teams grow, tools multiply, data fragments, responsibility blurs, and humans quietly become the connective tissue holding everything together. That works — until it becomes fragile.</p>
          <p>Our work is about replacing that fragility with systems that operate reliably — whether or not anyone is watching.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE FOUNDER -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[38%_62%] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Image -->
        <div>
          <img src="/images/sk8.jpeg" alt="Sardar Azimov" class="block mx-auto" style="max-height: 520px; width: auto; border-radius: 10px;" />
        </div>
        <!-- Right: Content -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-5">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em]" style="color: #001D52;">
            Rooted in business, not just code.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-black text-base leading-relaxed">Sardar mastered automation and AI out of necessity — to scale output without burning<br>teams out.</p>
          <p class="text-black text-base leading-relaxed">Every system designed starts with business impact, asking:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full shrink-0 mt-1.5" style="background-color: #CFFF15;"></span>
              <span class="text-black text-base leading-relaxed">Where is human effort being wasted on work that shouldn't require humans?</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full shrink-0 mt-1.5" style="background-color: #CFFF15;"></span>
              <span class="text-black text-base leading-relaxed">Where is risk hiding inside a manual step?</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full shrink-0 mt-1.5" style="background-color: #CFFF15;"></span>
              <span class="text-black text-base leading-relaxed">What should stay human — and why?</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full shrink-0 mt-1.5" style="background-color: #CFFF15;"></span>
              <span class="text-black text-base leading-relaxed">What should never be automated?</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <!-- Quote line -->
          <div class="flex items-stretch gap-3">
            <div class="w-[3px] rounded-full shrink-0" style="background-color: #001D52;"></div>
            <p class="text-black text-base leading-relaxed">Judgment comes before technology. Always.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-black text-base leading-relaxed">Leading at the architecture level to ensure solutions stay grounded in business reality,<br>rather than technical novelty.</p>
          <!-- Name & title -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-2">
            <span class="font-bold text-black">Sardar Azimov</span>
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full shrink-0" style="background-color: #001D52;"></span>
            <span class="font-bold text-black">Founder &amp; Principal</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW THE TEAM WORKS -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Heading block -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-block">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy"></div>
              <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-navy tracking-[0.2em]">The Studio</p>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy mb-3 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-center">
              How the team works
            </h2>
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-10"></div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
          <p class="text-black italic">
            Skief Labs operates as a studio — deliberately small,<br>deliberately senior.
          </p>
          <p>Projects are architected at a senior level and executed by<br>trusted specialists in data engineering, automation, and AI<br>systems. Every engagement is reviewed for clarity,<br>stability, and ownership before it's delivered.</p>
          <p class="text-black font-semibold">There are no junior handoffs. No hidden subcontracting.<br>No black boxes.</p>
          <p>Clients always know who is responsible for what — and<br>why decisions are being made.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Callout box -->
        <div class="flex items-stretch gap-4 mt-10">
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p class="text-black text-sm italic leading-relaxed py-1 text-left">Every system we deliver is fully documented and handed over — so your team never<br>depends on us to understand what was built or why.</p>
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto reveal">
        <!-- Heading block -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-block">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy"></div>
              <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-navy tracking-[0.2em]">The Edge</p>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy mb-3 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-center">
              What makes us different
            </h2>
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-10"></div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
          <p>We are not an agency.<br>We are not freelancers.<br>We are not traditional consultants.</p>
          <p class="text-black font-semibold">We build systems — two specific kinds — with deliberate restraint.</p>
          <p>We work on problems we're genuinely equipped to solve.<br>We don't take on engagements to fill capacity. We say no<br>when something shouldn't be built.</p>
          <p>We document everything so clients never need to come<br>back for something they already paid for.</p>
          <p>We measure success by how little our clients need us<br>over time — not by how much they do.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Callout box -->
        <div class="flex items-stretch gap-4 mt-10">
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p class="text-black text-sm italic leading-relaxed py-1 text-left">That last point is the most important one. Dependency is easy to create and profitable<br>to maintain. We've chosen not to.</p>
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
